      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRANSFORMATION (1) is progressing well scoring last time out (19.89) at Angle Park and bringing up her 2nd career win. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Well placed and can measure up. COBALT WINTER (8) was below best last time finishing sixth at Angle Park, but prior to that had been racing well including a TG1-4W win two back at Angle Park. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Can improve sharply here. ASTER BALLISTIC (5) has a strong overall record having three wins and three places from nine starts including a last start second (19.73) over 350m at Murray Bridge Straight. Has a good overall strike-rate and can find the frame here. ELLSWORTH (7) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
